A damage type caused by freezing temperatures and frigid climate.
&nbsp;
Cold Damage is always _Endurable_. 
&nbsp;
When removing _Vulnerable_, you may inflict an equivalent amount of _Frigid_ instead of increasing Damage if you deal Cold Damage.
&nbsp;
If a character is _Downed_ by Cold Damage, inflict the following _Wounds_ based on the roll:
 1-2: Frigidt_ 1
 3-4:Frigidst_ 2
5-6Frigidost_ 3

A damage type caused by jolts of lightning and electricity.
&nbsp;
Lightning Damage is always _Endurable_. Any _Area_ Attack that deals Lightning Damage splits Damage and Status evenly between all targets rather than deal the listed amount of Damage/Status to all creatures.
&nbsp;
When removing _Vulnerable_, you may inflict an equivalent amount of _Shocked_ instead of increasing Damage if you deal Lightning Damage.
&nbsp;
If a character is _Downed_ by Lightning Damage, inflict the following _Wounds_ based on the roll:
 1-2: _Shocked_ 1
 3-4: _Shocked_ 2
5-6: _Shocked_ 3
